OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother largely sunny and hot
OL,6,Fday, but possibly turning murky in the
OL,7,FIsles of Scilly, with low cloud
OL,8,Freaching west Cornwall by the evening.
OL,9,FFreshening easterly winds, gusty in
OL,10,Fplaces. Isolated showers from late
OL,11,Fafternoon, with a risk of thunder.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA bright and very warm
OL,14,Fevening for many, however cloud
OL,15,Falready across the far west of
OL,16,FCornwall will spread eastwards
OL,17,Fovernight. Cooler than recent nights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
