OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA bright start in the east,
OL,6,Fbut thicker cloud already across the
OL,7,Ffar west will spread eastwards,
OL,8,Fperhaps with some showers in places.
OL,9,FStill very warm in the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FLargely
OL,12,Ffine and settled over the coming days,
OL,13,Fhowever it will turn cloudier from the
OL,14,Fwest at times, perhaps with some
OL,15,Fshowers on Thursday. Temperatures
OL,16,Fslowly returning to normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
